    <title>力扣第279场周赛题解</title>
    <url>/2022/02/08/%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%A3%E7%AC%AC279%E5%9C%BA%E5%91%A8%E8%B5%9B%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width=330 height=86 src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1371757760&auto=1&height=66"></iframe>

<h2 id="1-对奇偶下标分别排序"><a href="#1-对奇偶下标分别排序" class="headerlink" title="1.对奇偶下标分别排序"></a>1.<a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/sort-even-and-odd-indices-independently/">对奇偶下标分别排序</a></h2><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p>给你一个下标从0开始的整数数组 <code>nums</code> 。根据下述规则重排 <code>nums</code> 中的值：</p>
<ul>
<li>按<strong>非递增</strong>顺序排列 <code>nums</code> 奇数下标 上的所有值。</li>
<li>按<strong>非递减</strong>顺序排列 <code>nums</code> 偶数下标 上的所有值。</li>
</ul>
<p>返回重排 <code>nums</code> 的值之后形成的数组。</p>
<h3 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><p>水题, 略</p>
<h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">sortEvenOdd</span><span class="hljs-params">(vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; nums)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        priority_queue&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; l1;<br>        priority_queue&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>,vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;,greater&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;&gt;l2;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n=nums.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i&amp;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)l1.<span class="hljs-built_in">push</span>(nums[i]);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> l2.<span class="hljs-built_in">push</span>(nums[i]);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i&amp;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)nums[i]=l1.<span class="hljs-built_in">top</span>(),l1.<span class="hljs-built_in">pop</span>();<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> nums[i]=l2.<span class="hljs-built_in">top</span>(),l2.<span class="hljs-built_in">pop</span>();<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> nums;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-重排数字的最小值"><a href="#2-重排数字的最小值" class="headerlink" title="2.重排数字的最小值"></a>2.<a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/smallest-value-of-the-rearranged-number/">重排数字的最小值</a></h2><h3 id="题目-1"><a href="#题目-1" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p>给你一个整数 <code>num</code> 。重排 <code>num</code> 中的各位数字，使其值<strong>最小化</strong>且不含<strong>任何</strong>前导零。</p>
<p>返回不含前导零且值最小的重排数字。</p>
<p>注意，重排各位数字后， <code>num</code> 的符号不会改变。</p>
<h3 id="题解-1"><a href="#题解-1" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><p><del>样例非常良心, 换做我就不会给负数样例</del></p>
<p>显然, 要将正负数分开考虑，负数直接将数字从大到小排就完事，正数先从小到大排，再将第一个非零数字与第一个数字互换即可</p>
<h3 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title">mystoi</span><span class="hljs-params">(string&amp;s)</span></span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> ret=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">char</span> c:s)&#123;<br>            ret=ret*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+c-<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ret;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title">great</span><span class="hljs-params">(string s)</span></span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">sort</span>(s.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),s.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>(),[](<span class="hljs-type">char</span> a,<span class="hljs-type">char</span> b)&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a&gt;b;&#125;);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">mystoi</span>(s);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title">les</span><span class="hljs-params">(string s)</span></span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">sort</span>(s.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),s.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>());<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;s.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();i++)<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i]!=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)&#123;<span class="hljs-built_in">swap</span>(s[i],s[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]);<span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;&#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">mystoi</span>(s);<br>    &#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-title">smallestNumber</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> num)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(num&lt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> -<span class="hljs-built_in">great</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">to_string</span>(-num));<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">les</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">to_string</span>(num));<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-设计位集"><a href="#3-设计位集" class="headerlink" title="3.设计位集"></a>3.<a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/design-bitset/">设计位集</a></h2><h3 id="题目-2"><a href="#题目-2" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p>位集 <code>Bitset</code> 是一种能以紧凑形式存储位的数据结构。</p>
<p>请你实现 <code>Bitset</code> 类。</p>
<p><code>Bitset(int size)</code> 用 <code>size</code> 个位初始化 <code>Bitset</code> ，所有位都是 0 。<br><code>void fix(int idx)</code> 将下标为 <code>idx</code> 的位上的值更新为 1 。如果值已经是 1 ，则不会发生任何改变。<br><code>void unfix(int idx)</code> 将下标为 <code>idx</code> 的位上的值更新为 0 。如果值已经是 0 ，则不会发生任何改变。<br><code>void flip()</code> 翻转 <code>Bitset</code> 中每一位上的值。换句话说，所有值为 0 的位将会变成 1 ，反之亦然。<br><code>boolean all()</code> 检查  <code>Bitset</code> 中<strong>每一位</strong>的值是否都是 1 。如果满足此条件，返回 <code>true</code> ；否则，返回 <code>false</code> 。<br><code>boolean one()</code> 检查  <code>Bitset</code> 中 是否<strong>至少一位</strong>的值是 1 。如果满足此条件，返回 <code>true</code> ；否则，返回 <code>false</code> 。<br><code>int count()</code> 返回 <code>Bitset</code> 中值为 1 的位的 总数 。<br><code>String toString()</code> 返回 <code>Bitset</code> 的当前组成情况。注意，在结果字符串中，第 <code>i</code> 个下标处的字符应该与 <code>Bitset</code> 中的第 <code>i</code> 位一致。</p>
<h3 id="题解-2"><a href="#题解-2" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><p>暴力模拟，勉强能卡过。。。</p>
<h3 id="代码-2"><a href="#代码-2" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn=<span class="hljs-number">1e5</span>+<span class="hljs-number">7</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Bitset</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> buf[maxn/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>+<span class="hljs-number">3</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n,cnt;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">char</span> <span class="hljs-title">num</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> idx)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (buf[idx/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>]&gt;&gt;(idx%<span class="hljs-number">8</span>))&amp;<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Bitset</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> size) &#123;n=size,cnt=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;=size/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i++)buf[i]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">fix</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> idx)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">num</span>(idx))<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>        ++cnt, buf[idx/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>]|=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;idx%<span class="hljs-number">8</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">unfix</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> idx)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(!<span class="hljs-built_in">num</span>(idx))<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>        --cnt, buf[idx/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>]&amp;=~(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;idx%<span class="hljs-number">8</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">flip</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        cnt=n-cnt;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;=n/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i++)buf[i]=~buf[i];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">all</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> cnt==n;&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">one</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> cnt&gt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">count</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> cnt;&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">string <span class="hljs-title">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        string ret;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++)ret.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>+<span class="hljs-built_in">num</span>(i));<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ret;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="4-移除所有载有违禁货物车厢所需的最少时间"><a href="#4-移除所有载有违禁货物车厢所需的最少时间" class="headerlink" title="4.移除所有载有违禁货物车厢所需的最少时间"></a>4.<a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/minimum-time-to-remove-all-cars-containing-illegal-goods/">移除所有载有违禁货物车厢所需的最少时间</a></h2><h3 id="题目-3"><a href="#题目-3" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p>给你一个下标从 0 开始的二进制字符串 <code>s</code> ，表示一个列车车厢序列。 <code>s[i] = &#39;0&#39;</code> 表示第 <code>i</code> 节车厢 不 含违禁货物，而 <code>s[i] = &#39;1&#39;</code> 表示第 <code>i</code> 节车厢含违禁货物。</p>
<p>作为列车长，你需要清理掉所有载有违禁货物的车厢。你可以不限次数执行下述三种操作中的任意一个：</p>
<ul>
<li>从列车 左 端移除一节车厢（即移除 <code>s[0]</code>），用去 1 单位时间。</li>
<li>从列车 右 端移除一节车厢（即移除 <code>s[s.length - 1]</code>），用去 1 单位时间。</li>
<li>从列车车厢序列的 任意位置 移除一节车厢，用去 2 单位时间。</li>
</ul>
<p>返回移除所有载有违禁货物车厢所需要的 最少 单位时间数。</p>
<p><strong>注意</strong>，空的列车车厢序列视为没有车厢含违禁货物。</p>
<h3 id="题解-3"><a href="#题解-3" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><p>假设 <code>left[i]</code> 为从左边开始移除第 <code>i</code> 个违禁品需要的最少时间， <code>right[i]</code> 为从右边开始移除第 <code>i</code> 个违禁品需要的最少时间，<br>那么总的最小时间为 <code>Min(left[i]+right[i+1])</code> 。</p>
<h3 id="代码-3"><a href="#代码-3" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">minimumTime</span><span class="hljs-params">(string s)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">pos1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)</span></span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> len=s.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;len;i++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i]==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>)pos1.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n=pos1.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>()<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">right</span><span class="hljs-params">(n+<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)</span></span>;<br>        right[n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=n;i&gt;=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i--)&#123;<br>            right[i]=len+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>-pos1[i];<br>            right[i]=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(right[i],right[i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]+<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> ans=<span class="hljs-number">1e9</span>+<span class="hljs-number">7</span>,left=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;<br>            ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(left+right[i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>],ans);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i&lt;n)left=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(pos1[i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>],left+<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ans;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="提示"><a href="#提示" class="headerlink" title="提示"></a>提示</h2><p>以上均不是最优解，但是能通过测试（毕竟比赛时看不到运行效率）</p>
]]></content>
